WEBVTT

00:03.208 --> 00:04.675
Over there! I saw him!

00:04.677 --> 00:05.776
This way, Detectives.

00:05.778 --> 00:06.844
What do we got?

00:06.846 --> 00:08.345
Male bleeding heavily
from his abdomen.

00:08.347 --> 00:10.614
EMTs are working
on him now.

00:12.784 --> 00:14.251
Hey, is he talking?

00:14.253 --> 00:15.486
He's circling the drain.

00:15.488 --> 00:16.487
What's his name?
Lee.

00:16.489 --> 00:18.622
Lee, do you know
who did this to you?

00:18.624 --> 00:20.257
- Losing him.
- Sir?

00:20.259 --> 00:22.893
If he knows, he ain't saying.

00:22.895 --> 00:24.628
Detectives.

00:24.630 --> 00:26.063
They have the perp in custody.

00:26.065 --> 00:28.332
Where is he?

00:28.334 --> 00:30.201
This way.

00:30.203 --> 00:32.302
Step back. Hey,
step back, everyone.

00:32.305 --> 00:33.470
Get back!

00:33.472 --> 00:34.872
At least tell me he's dead.
What?

00:34.874 --> 00:36.040
At least tell me he's dead.

00:36.042 --> 00:37.541
At least tell me
that monkey's dead.

00:37.543 --> 00:40.244
Yeah, he's dead.
You owning it?

00:40.246 --> 00:42.346
I guess I am,
though I got regrets.

00:42.348 --> 00:44.748
That's good to hear.

00:44.750 --> 00:46.650
I regret I couldn't see
he was just a old ape.

00:46.652 --> 00:49.720
Wanted to get me
a young frisky one!

00:49.722 --> 00:50.988
The only ape around here
is you, buddy.

00:50.990 --> 00:53.657
Let him out!

00:53.659 --> 00:56.126
Get the racist out of here!

00:56.128 --> 00:57.828
You have the right
to remain silent.

00:57.830 --> 00:59.863
I got a right to live
in a monkey-free country!

00:59.865 --> 01:00.772
Lock this up!

01:00.796 --> 01:01.967
Anything you say may
be used against you.

01:01.968 --> 01:04.367
Yeah, what I say is
go back to Africa!

01:04.370 --> 01:05.569
Shut up.

01:13.446 --> 01:15.246
You can't terminate
me for this.

01:15.248 --> 01:19.016
You don't tell me
what I can and cannot do.

01:19.018 --> 01:20.818
All right, shouldn't.

01:20.820 --> 01:23.787
Devin, it's not his choice,
it's department policy.

01:23.789 --> 01:25.656
You test positive for drugs,
you're out.

01:25.658 --> 01:26.824
Drugs, Sid?

01:26.826 --> 01:29.198
Yeah, marijuana's still drugs
in the NYPD.

01:29.199 --> 01:31.066
I had part of an edible
at the Denver airport.

01:31.068 --> 01:32.868
Bought in Colorado,
used in Colorado,

01:32.870 --> 01:34.636
left behind in Colorado.

01:34.638 --> 01:36.171
Which is legal--
I know, you told us.

01:36.173 --> 01:37.606
And you say that
like it doesn't matter.

01:37.608 --> 01:39.875
No, I say it like
it's a pain-in-the-ass excuse,

01:39.877 --> 01:41.443
which is all it is.

01:41.445 --> 01:43.745
What's legal say?

01:43.747 --> 01:45.080
That question's
above your rank.

01:45.082 --> 01:47.149
That question's like life
or death to me right now.

01:47.151 --> 01:49.151
Only life or death's
life or death.

01:49.153 --> 01:51.386
What's their take?

01:51.388 --> 01:53.288
They don't have one yet.
There's no precedent.

01:53.290 --> 01:54.990
But you, you have one?

01:54.992 --> 01:56.958
Your take is to just can my ass.

01:56.960 --> 01:58.093
It is still illegal

01:58.095 --> 02:01.029
in the NYPD,
in all city agencies,

02:01.031 --> 02:03.565
under state and federal law.

02:03.567 --> 02:05.567
I can't just look
the other way, Devin,

02:05.569 --> 02:08.804
because you decided
a Rocky Mountain high is okay.

02:08.806 --> 02:10.005
Now jokes?

02:10.840 --> 02:12.340
Hi, everyone.

02:12.342 --> 02:13.809
We got a little wrinkle.

02:13.811 --> 02:15.510
I hate that phrase.

02:15.512 --> 02:18.113
Okay. I got bad news. Better?

02:18.115 --> 02:19.815
Our mayor got wind

02:19.817 --> 02:21.983
of Chief Jones's predicament
and wants in.

02:21.985 --> 02:23.018
"Wants in"?

02:23.020 --> 02:24.519
She's very pro-legalization.

02:24.521 --> 02:26.321
She wants in on the next move.

02:26.323 --> 02:29.291
It's an NYPD matter.

02:29.293 --> 02:31.860
There's no room on the bus.
She leaks this to the press,

02:31.862 --> 02:33.795
we're gonna need
a much bigger bus.

02:33.797 --> 02:34.863
She'd do that?

02:34.865 --> 02:36.498
You really want to find out?

