Come on! Stop!

02:51.815 --> 02:53.949
Police! Stop!

02:53.951 --> 02:55.484
- Hey!
- I got him!

02:56.385 --> 02:57.986
I got him! Hey!

02:58.821 --> 03:01.089
- Watch out!
- Hey!

03:01.924 --> 03:03.992
Hey!

03:03.994 --> 03:05.360
Police! Stop him!

03:05.362 --> 03:07.562
Hey, give me a hand!

03:07.564 --> 03:10.599
Help me! Come on!

03:18.307 --> 03:20.075
Don't move.

03:21.744 --> 03:23.011
Come on.

03:23.013 --> 03:26.014
Hey. You okay?

03:26.016 --> 03:28.016
No. I'm not okay. Hey!

03:28.018 --> 03:29.317
Take this.

03:29.319 --> 03:30.752
Yeah, you, numbnuts.

03:30.754 --> 03:33.021
I'm talking to you.
Come here.

03:37.260 --> 03:38.994
Skip Fuller.

03:38.996 --> 03:41.563
Yeah. You are?
Eddie Janko. Do you remember me?

03:41.565 --> 03:44.332
Oh, no. What? You're a cop?

03:44.334 --> 03:47.135
Oh, yeah, I'm a cop, and right
now, never happier to be one.

03:47.137 --> 03:48.303
Put your hands behind your back.

03:48.305 --> 03:49.971
Eddie. Eddie.
No, I got this.

03:49.973 --> 03:51.740
You got what?
What is this?

03:51.742 --> 03:52.974
You're under arrest.

03:52.976 --> 03:55.677
In violation of
New York penal code 195.10,

03:55.679 --> 03:57.212
titled "Refusing to aid
a police officer.

03:57.214 --> 03:58.476
No way.

03:58.500 --> 04:00.049
Yeah, way.
Put your hands behind your back.

04:00.050 --> 04:02.050
Whoa, whoa.
I didn't do anything.

04:02.052 --> 04:03.552
Exactly. Story of your life.

04:03.554 --> 04:04.920
Oh.
All right.

04:04.922 --> 04:06.354
Hey!
Now I'm adding

04:06.356 --> 04:07.722
an additional charge
of resisting arrest

04:07.724 --> 04:09.057
and obstructing

04:09.059 --> 04:11.059
governmental administration.

04:11.061 --> 04:12.427
You're gonna want
to start cooperating.

04:12.429 --> 04:13.528
Oh.

04:13.530 --> 04:16.430
This is funny, huh, Skip?
Real funny.

04:21.704 --> 04:23.438
I got this, Jamie.

04:23.440 --> 04:25.340
Come on, Skip. Let's go.

